summary: I am a professional Chef specialized in Traditional Italian and Czech food.  I have a very long experience in Italian authentic pizza baking. I also like Fusion cusine and I have very good skills in meat - fish selection and preparation, butchery and fish cutting included. In a kitchen i am able of teamworking and I have high resilance in stressfull working places. I am very curious about Learning new methods and cooking traditions. I have more den 15y of exsperience, 5 of wich I was in full charge of my restaurants. I speak Italian, Czech, German in a full proficiency and English in a basic but efficent working proficiency.
